  <div class="c-entry-hero__header-wrap">
    <h1 class="c-page-title">9 questions about climate change you were too embarrassed to ask</h1>

    
  </div>
  <p class="c-entry-summary p-dek">Basic answers to basic questions about global warming and the future climate.</p>

  
    <div class="c-byline">
  <span class="c-byline-wrapper">
    
      By
      <span class="c-byline__item">
        
          
          <a href="https://www.vox.com/authors/brad-plumer" data-analytics-link="author-name"><span class="c-byline__author-name">Brad Plumer</span></a>, <a href="https://www.vox.com/authors/brian-resnick" data-analytics-link="author-name"><span class="c-byline__author-name">Brian Resnick</span></a>, and <a href="https://www.vox.com/authors/umair-irfan" data-analytics-link="author-name"><span class="c-byline__author-name">Umair Irfan</span></a>
        
      </span>
      
        
          <span class="c-byline__item">
            
                Updated
            
            <time class="c-byline__item" data-ui="timestamp" datetime="2018-12-28T19:50:15">
  Dec 28, 2018,  2:50pm EST
</time>
          </span>
        
      
      
      
    
    
